data.description: Price improvement for quick sale! ASSUMABLE 4% MORTGAGE! This beautiful 4,000 sq ft home boasts 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a study, huge game room, media room, 3 car garage, and a large fenced-in yard with a tree-lined greenbelt out back! All of this on a cul-de-sac lot in a community with too many amenities to list- from 6 pools and water slides, to a stocked fishing pond and fitness center, there's not much more you could ask for. The tall ceilings, large rooms, and open-concept living make this a great home for large families and entertainers alike. The kitchen island and its granite countertops are the perfect gathering place for all- it is the ideal hub for cooking, family fun, and entertaining. The private, fully sodded backyard has plenty of room to make this the oasis of your dreams! Upstairs you'll find plenty of room for games, a music studio, and the media room, which is the perfect spot to watch a game or enjoy move night. The possibilities are endless in this amazing home!
